code: @Override public void delete(Integer postId, Integer revisionId) {     checkArgument(postId > 0, "Please define a post id").     checkArgument(revisionId > 0, "Please define a revision id").     this.getSpi().delete(this.getApiVersion(), postId, revisionId). }

@Override public PostRevision retrieve(Integer postId, Integer revisionId, Context context) {     checkArgument(postId > 0, "Please define a post id").     checkArgument(revisionId > 0, "Please define a revision id").     return this.getSpi().retrieveRevision(this.getApiVersion(), postId, revisionId, context). }

@Override public List<PostRevision> list(Integer postId, Context context) {     checkArgument(postId > 0, "Please define a post id").     return this.getSpi().list(this.getApiVersion(), postId, context). }
